description:
Welcome to the new Dumb Blonde Unrated, where you can expect things to get even dirtier, raunchier, and all around Bunnie-r. Jelly joins the show this week to talk about his new album 'Self Medicated', and the inspiration behind this quarantine born album. Jelly also gets real about what he really thinks about Bunnie's new fantasy, what his favorite song is currently, and how the collaborations on this new album came to be.
